《'''衝鋒陷陣'''》（{{lang-en|''Charged Up''}}）是香港歌手[[黎明|黎明]]的[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]，全碟由[[雷頌德|雷頌德]]編曲及監製，於2002年5月21日由[[索尼音樂娛樂_(香港)|新力唱片]]首次發行<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.881903.com/highlight/2392818/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/5%E6%9C%8821%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|title = 5月21日之廣東歌|date = 2021-05-20|publisher = 商業電台|language = zh|accessdate = 2021-06-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210605022309/https://www.881903.com/highlight/2392818/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/5%E6%9C%8821%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|archive-date = 2021-06-05|dead-url = no}}</ref>；歌曲〈衝鋒陷陣〉國語版是[[2002年國際足協世界盃|2002年國際足協世界盃]][[大中華|大中華]]區官方主題曲<ref>{{cite news|language = zh|url = https://collection.news/appledaily/articles/US7W7XZOMJN4THDHNCYMGA55H4|title = 唱世盃主題曲任有線大使 黎明唔怕得罪無線|publisher = 蘋果日報|author = 何永寧|date = 2002-03-27|accessdate = 2022-03-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830195847/https://collection.news/appledaily/articles/US7W7XZOMJN4THDHNCYMGA55H4|archive-date = 2021-08-30|dead-url = no}}</ref>，由雷頌德作曲、[[周耀輝|周耀輝]]填詞、黎明主唱<ref>{{Cite book | author = 周耀輝、高偉雲 | title = 多重奏: 香港流行音樂聲像的全球流動 | location = 香港 | publisher = 香港中文大學出版社 | date = 2015 | pages = 24－26 | ISBN = 9629965879| language = zh}}</ref>，於2002年3月26日在全球各大傳媒電台啟播<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.hkce.com/press/release/2002/page25_big5.htm |title = 有線電視與Sony Music公布世界盃合作協議 黎明世界盃大碟(中港台區)宣傳歌曲「衝鋒陷陣」昨日全球首播 |date = 2002-03-26 |publisher = 有線電視 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-09-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200927060220/http://www.hkce.com/press/release/2002/page25_big5.htm |archive-date = 2020-09-27 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，同時亦收錄於2002年4月發行的世界盃主題曲大碟<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.discogs.com/Various-The-Official-Album-Of-The-2002-FIFA-World-Cup/release/7621854 |title = The Official Album Of The 2002 FIFA World Cup |date = 2002 |publisher = Discogs |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200927034228/https://www.discogs.com/Various-The-Official-Album-Of-The-2002-FIFA-World-Cup/release/7621854 |archive-date = 2020-09-27 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==背景及製作==
《衝鋒陷陣》是配合2002年國際足協世界盃而推出的音樂作品，新力唱片於2002年1月1日凌晨宣布成為該年度世界盃的指定品牌，由黎明代表中國、香港、台灣主唱大會主題曲，這首歌的國語版本與其他各國歌手主唱的版本，一同收錄於《The Official Album Of The 2002 FIFA World Cup》<ref>{{cite news|language =zh|author =蔡如玉、梁詠怡|url =https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20020102/4YTUZ3D36HVC4KYNAZYUFSZKHY/|title =唱世盃國語版主題曲露一手 黎明炫耀踢波兩度撻Q|publisher =蘋果日報|date =2002-01-02|accessdate =2021-06-17|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210617120645/https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20020102/4YTUZ3D36HVC4KYNAZYUFSZKHY/|archive-date =2021-06-17|dead-url =yes}}</ref>，歌曲音樂短片在[[香港大球場|香港大球場]]拍攝，內容包括踢足球、打乒乓球、為中國隊打氣及一些的士高氣氛高漲的畫面<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://ent.enorth.com.cn/system/2002/05/08/000325743.shtml |title = 黎明為世界盃主題曲拍攝MV動感十足 |date = 2002-05-08 |publisher = 北方網 |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2020-09-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20021031080142/http://ent.enorth.com.cn/system/2002/05/08/000325743.shtml |archive-date = 2002-10-31 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.southcn.com/ent/yulefirst/200204110474.htm |title = 黎明結緣世界盃好運不斷 |date = 2002-04-11 |publisher = 南方網 |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2020-09-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20020918115714/http://www.southcn.com/ent/yulefirst/200204110474.htm |archive-date = 2002-09-18 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，短片於2002年5月20日在一所的士高舉行首播會<ref>{{cite news|language =zh|url =http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1146969/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1|title =黎明《衝鋒陷陣》為中國隊打氣|publisher =星島日報|date =2002-05-21|accessdate =2019-11-16|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20191116074008/http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1146969/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1|archive-date =2019-11-16|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。粵語歌曲〈衝鋒陷陣〉收錄於《衝鋒陷陣》迷你專輯，專輯同時收錄了歌曲〈最美時光〉，這是[[香港公益金|香港公益金]]30週年主題曲，由黎明作曲及主唱，歌曲名字於1998年5月14日由當時的[[香港特別行政區行政長官|香港特別行政區行政長官]]夫人[[董趙洪娉|董趙洪娉]]從3個候選名字中選出，她認為無論施與受，只要有善事，就會有美好時光，因此選擇以「最美時光」為歌曲命名<ref>{{cite news |language =zh|url =https://i.imgur.com/aIwbonB.jpg|title =黎明、特首夫人及公益金負責人主持公益金踏入三十周年揭幕典禮|publisher=明報|author =依玲 |date =1998-05-15|accessdate =2021-12-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221114944/https://i.imgur.com/aIwbonB.jpg|archive-date = 2021-12-21|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，專輯的宣傳海報以中國國旗的紅色為主色，黎明以足球員造型擺出射球的姿勢，海報下方展示出「LEON世界盃《衝鋒陷陣》」、「衝鋒陷陣（廣東版）」、「最美時光」等字句<ref>{{cite news|language =zh|url =http://paper.wenweipo.com/2002/06/02/EN0206020022.htm|title =《衝鋒陷陣》海報有瑕疵|publisher =文匯報|author =秋子|date =2002-06-02|accessdate =2019-11-16|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20191116071829/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2002/06/02/EN0206020022.htm|archive-date =2019-11-16|dead-url =no}}</ref>，建議零售價為港幣29元<ref>{{cite news|language = zh|url = https://i.imgur.com/6ysRhUw.jpg|title = 現代音像 震撼全城|publisher = 蘋果日報|pages = C9 |date = 2002-05-21|accessdate = 2022-03-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220327121247/https://i.imgur.com/6ysRhUw.jpg|archive-date = 2022-03-27|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

